post_text:
DPS is seeking volunteers to assemble meals and to accompany a driver to deliver meals to households. #InThisTogetherOhio #DPSRises

Below are four requirements of all volunteers:
Volunteer is under the age of 50;
Volunteer does not reside with a person over 50 years of age (or regularly comes into contact with such a person);
Volunteer is over the age of 18 or volunteering under the supervision of a parent/legal guardian;
And in the past 14 days, volunteer has not had a fever, cough, or shortness of breath.

If you meet the above criteria and are willing to assist, please complete this questionnaire: bit.ly/dpssupport

New masks and gloves provided. If you have any questions please email DPSSupt@daytonpublic.com.

